Synod whisper cells have established a clandestine courier network through the Glasswind Belt, using it to move contraband past the Reach Warden inspection points. Couriers carry routing information, ritual keepers maintain the rite infrastructure that disguises the shipments, and lookouts monitor Warden patrol patterns. Eliminate one of each to break the current cell's operational capacity.
The Synod whisper cell courier network through the Glasswind Belt has been disrupted. The contraband routing chain is broken, the ritual concealment infrastructure has collapsed, and the lookout network monitoring Warden patrols has been cleared. The Warden patrol leader has forwarded the disruption report to the Midgaard Violet Compact registry for cross-reference against known Synod cell activity.

